da5-df13-a3af-bdb7f7130000</link><description>“以色列马歇尔计划”将包括将所有有影响力的弥赛亚主义者连根拔起，消除所有吞噬国家资金的正统派和种族主义“反教育”机构，并平等以色列公民的所有权利和义务</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 03:38:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-plan-to-save-israel-from-crumbling-in-the-next-few-years/0000018f-ada5-df13-a3af-bdb7f7130000</guid></item><item><title>数千人在特拉维夫和海法抗议政府，呼吁释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article-live/gantz-and-blinken-speak-about-rafah-idf-intercepts-aerial-target-in-northern-israel/0000018f-ad57-d8a2-a3cf-add7eb670000</link><description>以色列国防军在病毒视频中识别出蒙面男子威胁在加沙发动军事政变 ■ 西班牙国防部长称加沙战争是“真正的种族灭绝” ■ 以色列军队称袭击了黎巴嫩南部的真主党目标 ■ 叙利亚报道称，两名真主党成员在以色列附近的一次袭击中丧生霍姆斯 ■ 中情局、摩萨德首席与卡塔尔总理会面后重启人质处理工作</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 May 2024 01:29:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article-live/gantz-and-blinken-speak-about-rafah-idf-intercepts-aerial-target-in-northern-israel/0000018f-ad57-d8a2-a3cf-add7eb670000</guid></item><item><title>尽管有灾难警告，以色列南部仍在建设“圣经带”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-bible-belt-is-in-the-works-in-israels-south-despite-warnings-of-disaster/0000018f-ac7a-d8a2-a3cf-acfb5a2f0000</link><description>31 号高速公路沿线在内盖夫的阿拉德和拉哈特之间，规划了 9 个新的城市和乡村地点，其中 4 个指定为宗教社区。严重经济和环境影响的警告被忽视</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 22:57:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-bible-belt-is-in-the-works-in-israels-south-despite-warnings-of-disaster/0000018f-ac7a-d8a2-a3cf-acfb5a2f0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院的裁决并未束缚以色列在拉法的手脚，但以色列必须优先考虑人道主义局势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article/.premium/icj-does-not-order-stop-to-rafah-campaign-but-israel-must-prioritize-civilian-safety/0000018f-ac41-dca9-a5cf-bc41cf8d0000</link><description>国际法院对拉法的裁决并不是停止所有行动的明确命令，但法院明确表示以色列必须将平民安全放在第一位。以色列领导人应该听取法院的意见，而不是努力剥夺法院的合法性</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 21:25:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article/.premium/icj-does-not-order-stop-to-rafah-campaign-but-israel-must-prioritize-civilian-safety/0000018f-ac41-dca9-a5cf-bc41cf8d0000</guid></item><item><title>一个对死亡和破坏如此漠不关心的社会已经输掉了战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-society-so-indifferent-to-death-and-destruction-has-already-lost-the-war/0000018f-a53d-d807-a7df-a53fb0370000</link><description>只有那些弱者才觉得有必要释放如此夸张的武力，并对数千名儿童被杀害漠不关心，就像以色列在加沙所做的那样</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 21:20:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-25/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-society-so-indifferent-to-death-and-destruction-has-already-lost-the-war/0000018f-a53d-d807-a7df-a53fb0370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的新叙事：战争就是幸福</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-new-narrative-war-is-bliss/0000018f-abdf-dfc6-a3ef-bfdfb7e60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 19:07:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-24/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-new-narrative-war-is-bliss/0000018f-abdf-dfc6-a3ef-bfdfb7e60000</guid></item><item><title>国际法专家称，以色列司法部门的无能导致了海牙危机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/intl-law-experts-israeli-judiciarys-incompetence-contributed-to-crisis-at-the-hague/0000018f-aa55-d8a2-a3cf-aed7d3210000</link><description>专家表示，以色列司法部门在调查违反战争法、高级官员煽动加沙人等事件方面的记录不佳，这将使以色列很难在海牙声称自己正在认真调查。但改变方向还为时不晚</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 18:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-24/ty-article/.premium/intl-law-experts-israeli-judiciarys-incompetence-contributed-to-crisis-at-the-hague/0000018f-aa55-d8a2-a3cf-aed7d3210000</guid></item><item>